			[1292] paragraph ''
				StaticText 'This project aims to simplify and guide the way beginners make their first contribution. If you are looking to make your first contribution, follow the steps below.'

				[1294] emphasis ''
					StaticText "If you're not comfortable with command line,"

			[1298] heading "If you don't have git on your machine, install it."

				[1316] image ''
			[1317] paragraph ''

			[1320] paragraph ''
				StaticText 'For example:'
